    'en-UK':
      "Story time! You'll read 111 pages from a book. Once you start, please silently read all the pages as quickly as you can, while maintaining full comprehension, until you reach the end. Then we'll ask you a few questions about the story. On each page, press the SPACE bar for the next page. When you're ready, press SPACE.",
